txt.en: 'Good! This gives me plenty to experiment with.'
You have helped several people around town.\n\nIt is time to return to Eluna in Lhan Garan.
Eluna asked you to help folks around Lhan Garan.\n\nHelp people around Lhan Garan.

'I'm still trying to sort out why the Draig-l√ªth are here. When we left to settle Lhan Garan it was certainly a source of tension, but Talfryn secured the promise we'd be left alone. Let me look into this. Don't worry, I promise I'll keep safe.\n\n'Until I have news, could you help some folks around town?'
Eluna would like you to help folks around Lhan Garan.
'You have an uncanny knack for good timing, friend. I have news.'
